357
00:21:51,601 --> 00:21:54,354
<i>A fugitive inmate from Bagumbayan Prison</i>

358
00:21:54,438 --> 00:21:57,357
<i>was spotted earlier</i>
<i>this morning in San Dimas.</i>

359
00:21:57,441 --> 00:21:59,443
<i>Jet Santos reports.</i>

360
00:21:59,526 --> 00:22:02,154
[Jet] <i>This video was</i>
<i>captured by a San Dimas resident.</i>

361
00:22:02,237 --> 00:22:04,656
<i>The morning was quiet, when suddenly--</i>

362
00:22:04,740 --> 00:22:05,991
<i>consecutive explosions shook…</i>

363
00:22:06,074 --> 00:22:07,784
- [man] <i>What's that, man?</i>
- <i>…the residents</i>

364
00:22:07,868 --> 00:22:09,619
<i>- of this quiet town.</i>
- [man] <i>Man, what's that?</i>

365
00:22:09,703 --> 00:22:11,621
[Jet] <i>People in San Dimas had no idea</i>

366
00:22:11,705 --> 00:22:13,874
<i>that inside this closed</i>
<i>junk shop on Del Mundo Street,</i>

367
00:22:13,957 --> 00:22:17,461
<i>an inmate from Bagumbayan Prison,</i>

368
00:22:17,544 --> 00:22:21,006
<i>Edmundo Santiago,</i>
<i>also known as Edong, was hiding.</i>

369
00:22:21,089 --> 00:22:23,759
<i>A little past 10 AM,</i>
<i>while making their rounds,</i>

370
00:22:23,842 --> 00:22:27,054
<i>NLEA officers in</i>
<i>San Dimas spotted Santiago</i>

371
00:22:27,137 --> 00:22:29,514
<i>inside the junk shop.</i>

372
00:22:29,598 --> 00:22:33,435
<i>They didn't hesitate,</i>
<i>they stormed in to arrest him.</i>

373
00:22:33,518 --> 00:22:34,936
<i>According to NLEA's evaluation,</i>

374
00:22:35,020 --> 00:22:39,066
<i>Santiago seemed</i>
<i>prepared for a possible raid.</i>

375
00:22:39,149 --> 00:22:43,195
<i>They believe this was due</i>
<i>to the improvised explosive devices</i>

376
00:22:43,278 --> 00:22:45,530
<i>he had set off to escape.</i>

377
00:22:45,614 --> 00:22:49,451
<i>Still, NLEA considers</i>
<i>the operation a collateral success</i>

378
00:22:49,534 --> 00:22:54,206
<i>because it led to new,</i>
<i>valuable leads for the manhunt.</i>

379
00:22:54,289 --> 00:22:57,626
<i>Aside from no casualties</i>
<i>or injuries on the NLEA side,</i>

380
00:22:57,709 --> 00:22:59,503
<i>they reportedly managed to shoot Santiago.</i>

381
00:22:59,586 --> 00:23:02,255
<i>They believe he won't get far.</i>

382
00:23:02,339 --> 00:23:06,968
[tense music swells]

383
00:23:10,847 --> 00:23:13,433
[Liezel] You okay there, partner?

384
00:23:15,102 --> 00:23:16,978
