386
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:22,609
[foreboding music playing]

387
00:23:27,948 --> 00:23:28,949
[clicks]

388
00:23:34,121 --> 00:23:35,080
[clicking]

389
00:23:35,163 --> 00:23:39,334
[foreboding music continues]

390
00:23:41,670 --> 00:23:44,297
[Jet] <i>NLEA scores</i>
<i>a major intelligence gain</i>

391
00:23:44,381 --> 00:23:47,759
<i>with Santiago's hideout,</i>

392
00:23:47,843 --> 00:23:50,387
<i>reducing his area of interest</i>

393
00:23:50,470 --> 00:23:52,889
<i>and improving the odds of catching him</i>

394
00:23:52,973 --> 00:23:55,016
<i>before the week ends.</i>

395
00:23:55,100 --> 00:23:57,561
<i>Jet Santos, Prime News PH.</i>

396
00:23:57,644 --> 00:24:01,064
[foreboding music crescendos]

397
00:24:02,065 --> 00:24:03,483
<i>Are you fighting with Attorney</i>

398
00:24:03,567 --> 00:24:06,444
<i>because she doesn't</i>
<i>believe Edong is the killer?</i>

399
00:24:06,528 --> 00:24:09,072
